{{CatTrack}}
{{Wikipedia category|hidden=yes|tracking=yes}}
This category contains all pages labeled with {{tlg|Better source}}, {{tl|Obsolete source}}, {{tl|Primary sources}}, {{tl|Unreliable sources}}, {{tl|Verify credibility}}, {{tl|Third-party}}, and {{tl|Third-party-inline}} and exists primarily for bot-based monitoring of articles which don't have reliable sources. By-month categories are located in [[:Category:Articles lacking reliable references]].
